#Retail Business Intelligence Dashboard

##Project Overview
This project presents an interactive business intelligence solution developed in Power BI for analyzing retail sales data. 
The dashboard provides insights into sales performance, payment methods, product categories, and manufacturer countries through a multi-page analytical report.

##Tools
- Microsoft Power BI
- DAX
- Data Modeling
- Business Intelligence
- Data Visualization

##Methods Applied
- Data modeling using related tables
- Calendar table creation for time-based analysis
- DAX measures for KPI calculation
- Interactive dashboard design
- Multi-page report navigation
- Dynamic chart switching
- Sales and payment method analysis
- Product category analysis
- Manufacturer country analysis
- Interactive filtering and drill-down exploration

##Dashboard Structure
Page 1 – Sales and Payment Analysis: Analysis of sales performance, payment methods, and key business indicators.
Page 2 – Sales Structure Analysis: Analysis of product categories, sales distribution, and customer purchasing patterns.
Page 3 – Manufacturer Country Analysis: Analysis of product origins, manufacturer countries, and international sales structure.

##Results
The dashboard enables comprehensive analysis of retail operations through interactive visualizations, KPI monitoring, and multidimensional exploration of sales data. 
Users can navigate between report pages, apply filters, and switch between alternative visual representations to gain deeper business insights.
